snippet: Debbie Dunn, who was in the pool of runners for the 4x400-meter Olympic relay team at the Summer Games, has removed herself from the team.
abstract: Debbie Dunn, sprinter who qualified for the United States Olympic track team, removes herself from the team after a positive drug test at the Olympic trials.
lead_paragraph: Debbie Dunn, who was in the pool of runners for the 4x400-meter Olympic relay team at the Summer Games, has removed herself from the team.
